{"an7.29:0.1":"Anguttara Nikaya 7.29 ","an7.29:0.2":"3. Vajjisattakavagga ","an7.29:0.3":"Dutiyaparihanisutta ","an7.29:1.1":"“Sattime, bhikkhave, dhamma upasakassa parihanaya samvattanti. ","an7.29:1.2":"Katame satta? ","an7.29:1.3":"Bhikkhudassanam hapeti, ","an7.29:1.4":"saddhammassavanam pamajjati, ","an7.29:1.5":"adhisile na sikkhati, ","an7.29:1.6":"appasadabahulo hoti, ","an7.29:1.7":"bhikkhusu theresu ceva navesu ca majjhimesu ca uparambhacitto dhammam sunati randhagavesi, ","an7.29:1.8":"ito bahiddha dakkhineyyam gavesati, ","an7.29:1.9":"tattha ca pubbakaram karoti. ","an7.29:1.10":"Ime kho, bhikkhave, satta dhamma upasakassa parihanaya samvattanti. ","an7.29:2.1":"Sattime, bhikkhave, dhamma upasakassa aparihanaya samvattanti. ","an7.29:2.2":"Katame satta? ","an7.29:2.3":"Bhikkhudassanam na hapeti, ","an7.29:2.4":"saddhammassavanam nappamajjati, ","an7.29:2.5":"adhisile sikkhati, ","an7.29:2.6":"pasadabahulo hoti, ","an7.29:2.7":"bhikkhusu theresu ceva navesu ca majjhimesu ca anuparambhacitto dhammam sunati na randhagavesi, ","an7.29:2.8":"na ito bahiddha dakkhineyyam gavesati, ","an7.29:2.9":"idha ca pubbakaram karoti. ","an7.29:2.10":"Ime kho, bhikkhave, satta dhamma upasakassa aparihanaya samvattanti”ti. ","an7.29:2.11":"Idamavoca bhagava. ","an7.29:2.12":"Idam vatvana sugato athaparam etadavoca sattha: ","an7.29:3.1":"“Dassanam bhavitattanam, ","an7.29:3.2":"Yo hapeti upasako; ","an7.29:3.3":"Savananca ariyadhammanam, ","an7.29:3.4":"Adhisile na sikkhati. ","an7.29:4.1":"Appasado ca bhikkhusu, ","an7.29:4.2":"bhiyyo bhiyyo pavaddhati; ","an7.29:4.3":"Uparambhakacitto ca, ","an7.29:4.4":"saddhammam sotumicchati. ","an7.29:5.1":"Ito ca bahiddha annam, ","an7.29:5.2":"dakkhineyyam gavesati; ","an7.29:5.3":"Tattheva ca pubbakaram, ","an7.29:5.4":"yo karoti upasako. ","an7.29:6.1":"Ete kho parihaniye, ","an7.29:6.2":"satta dhamme sudesite; ","an7.29:6.3":"Upasako sevamano, ","an7.29:6.4":"saddhamma parihayati. ","an7.29:7.1":"Dassanam bhavitattanam, ","an7.29:7.2":"Yo na hapeti upasako; ","an7.29:7.3":"Savananca ariyadhammanam, ","an7.29:7.4":"Adhisile ca sikkhati. ","an7.29:8.1":"Pasado cassa bhikkhusu, ","an7.29:8.2":"bhiyyo bhiyyo pavaddhati; ","an7.29:8.3":"Anuparambhacitto ca, ","an7.29:8.4":"saddhammam sotumicchati. ","an7.29:9.1":"Na ito bahiddha annam, ","an7.29:9.2":"dakkhineyyam gavesati; ","an7.29:9.3":"Idheva ca pubbakaram, ","an7.29:9.4":"yo karoti upasako. ","an7.29:10.1":"Ete kho aparihaniye, ","an7.29:10.2":"Satta dhamme sudesite; ","an7.29:10.3":"Upasako sevamano, ","an7.29:10.4":"Saddhamma na parihayati”ti. ","an7.29:10.5":"Navamam. "}